A temporary solution I've figured out is changing your party to invite-only and back to open or visa versa. This seems to reset the party and fixes the problem! Though this sometimes doesn't work so what I usually do is get someone else to create the party and repeat the original process.

tl;dr
Switch your party to invite-only and back to open {{sticker:sg-lux-2}}

Thanks for your efforts, certainly a sucky situation for everyone to go into the weekend with (Including you guys!).

Hope the team can come up with something, to save everyone's weekend!

